      <title>Linux操作系统</title>
      <link href="/2025/04/11/Linux%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/"/>
      <url>/2025/04/11/Linux%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1><center> <em><strong>Linux</strong></em> </center></h1><h2 id="一、基本指令">一、基本指令</h2><ol><li><p><strong>pwd</strong><br><code>hcy@hcy-virtual-machine:~$ pwd</code><br>这行代码的含义是查询当前文件夹下的路径<br><em><strong>eg：</strong></em><br>输出：<code>/home/hcy</code></p></li><li><p><strong>cd</strong><br><code>hcy@hcy-virtual-machine:~$ cd</code></p><ol><li><code>cd ..</code>  意思是回退到上一个文件夹目录</li><li><code>cd xxx</code> 意思是转移到该盘符</li></ol></li><li><p><strong>vim</strong></p><blockquote><p><em>注意！使用vim前需要下载！</em></p></blockquote><p><code>hcy@hcy-virtual-machine:~$ vim xxx.xxx</code><br>这段代码的含义是利用vim生成一个空的文件，文件名和后缀可以自己控制</p></li><li><p><strong>mkdir</strong><br><code>hcy@hcy-virtual-machine:~$ mkdir xxx</code><br>这段代码的含义是在当前目录下生成一个文件夹</p></li><li><p><strong>rmdir</strong><br><code>hcy@hcy-virtual-machine:~$ rmdir xxx</code><br>删除当前目录下的文件夹</p></li><li><p><strong>rm</strong><br><code>hcy@hcy-virtual-machine:~$ rm xxx.xxx</code><br>删除某个文件</p></li><li><p><strong>mv</strong><br><code>hcy@hcy-virtual-machine:~$ mv oldfile newfile</code><br>把旧文件移动到新文件上<br><code>hcy@hcy-virtual-machine:~$ mv filename ~/Document/</code><br>把文件移动到文件夹内</p></li><li><p><strong>ls</strong><br><code>hcy@hcy-virtual-machine:~$ ls</code><br>显示当前文件夹下所有的文件，后续加上<code>-l</code>可以查看每个文件的详细信息，以及读写权。</p></li></ol><hr><blockquote><p>以上是一些Ubuntu操作系统下控制台输入的一些基本能用的指令，需要了解全部指令可以自行百度百科</p></blockquote><h2 id="二、操作系统实例——银行家算法">二、操作系统实例——银行家算法</h2><ol><li><p><strong>银行家算法的介绍</strong><br>操作系统中有很多资源和进程，每个进程可能随时会申请资源，这种情况会导致操作系统死锁的发生，而银行家算法就是利用银行给客户借钱（分配资源）以及客户最后还钱（释放资源）进行排序（对进程调度），用来防止死锁的发生，保护各个程序能有序进行。</p></li><li><p><strong>银行家算法的主要思路</strong><br>银行家算法的根本目的在于确保分配资源的顺序是安全的，那么我们可以写一个程序来模拟一下银行家算法是怎么安排各个程序有序进行的。</p><blockquote><p>下面是银行家算法的Banker.hpp文件，描述了银行家算法类的结构</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">pragma</span> once</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">BankerAlgorithm</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">BankerAlgorithm</span>(<span class="type">int</span> num_processes, <span class="type">int</span> num_resources,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="type">const</span> std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; available,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="type">const</span> std::vector&lt;std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; alloc,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="type">const</span> std::vector&lt;std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; need);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 处理资源请求</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">request_resources</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> pid, <span class="type">const</span> std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; request)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 打印当前系统状态</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">print_state</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="type">const</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> num_processes_;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> num_resources_;</span><br><span class="line">    std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; available_;</span><br><span class="line">    std::vector&lt;std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt; alloc_;</span><br><span class="line">    std::vector&lt;std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt; need_;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 检查请求是否合法（request &lt;= need[pid] 且 request &lt;= available）</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">is_request_valid</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> pid, <span class="type">const</span> std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; request)</span> <span class="type">const</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 安全性检查算法</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">is_safe_state</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="type">const</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们可以看到类的私有成员有五个，分别是进程的个数<code>num_processes_</code>，资源的种类<code>num_resources_</code>；还有三个数组分别是<code>available[]</code>,<code>alloc_[][]</code>,<code>need_[][]</code>。<br>为什么有的数组是一维，而有的是二维呢？因为二维数组不仅要保存每个进程的<code>PID</code>还要保存需求或者分配的资源种类的数量。</p><p>我们还能发现类种有四个函数，分别实现了<code>处理资源请求</code>，<code>输出当前系统状态</code>，<code>检查请求是否合法</code>，<code>安全性检查四种功能</code>。我们接下来好好看看这四个功能具体的算法实现。</p><blockquote><p>以下是各个函数的实现：</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">BankerAlgorithm::is_request_valid</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> pid, <span class="type">const</span> std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; request)</span> <span class="type">const</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 检查请求是否超过进程需求</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; num_resources_; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (request[i] &gt; need_[pid][i]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 检查请求是否超过可用资源</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; num_resources_; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (request[i] &gt; available_[i]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们首先来看<code>检查请求是否合法</code>的函数，遍历所有的资源种类，判断进场需求每个种类的大小分别是否超过了需求<code>need_[pid][i]</code>，和剩余资源数量<code>available_[i]</code>的数目，如果超过了代表非法请求就返回<code>false</code>。</p> <figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">BankerAlgorithm::request_resources</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> pid, <span class="type">const</span> std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; request)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!<span class="built_in">is_request_valid</span>(pid, request)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        std::cerr &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;非法请求: 进程 P&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; pid &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; 请求超过需求或可用资源\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 试探性分配</span></span><br><span class="line">    std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; old_available = available_;</span><br><span class="line">    std::vector&lt;std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt; old_alloc = alloc_;</span><br><span class="line">    std::vector&lt;std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt; old_need = need_;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; num_resources_; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        available_[i] -= request[i];</span><br><span class="line">        alloc_[pid][i] += request[i];</span><br><span class="line">        need_[pid][i] -= request[i];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!<span class="built_in">is_safe_state</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 恢复原状态</span></span><br><span class="line">        available_ = old_available;</span><br><span class="line">        alloc_ = old_alloc;</span><br><span class="line">        need_ = old_need;</span><br><span class="line">        std::cerr &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;请求导致系统不安全，已回滚\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;资源分配成功，系统仍处于安全状态\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>处理资源请求</code>函数实现了“<strong>试着分配着看</strong>”这种思想，首先判断请求是否合法，如果合法就先把银行原来保存的内容用<code>old_</code>记录下来，接着把对应资源分别发给申请程序。接下来用<code>安全性检查函数</code>来判断这次“<strong>试着分配</strong>”的操作是否安全，如果不安全就把数据回滚为<code>old_</code>版本，如果分配成功则<code>return true;</code></p> <figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">BankerAlgorithm::is_safe_state</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="type">const</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; work = available_;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">std::vector&lt;<span class="type">bool</span>&gt; <span class="title">finish</span><span class="params">(num_processes_, <span class="literal">false</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; safe_sequence;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> count = <span class="number">0</span>; count &lt; num_processes_; ++count) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">bool</span> found = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; num_processes_; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (!finish[i]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">bool</span> can_allocate = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; num_resources_; ++j) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">if</span> (need_[i][j] &gt; work[j]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        can_allocate = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (can_allocate) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; num_resources_; ++j) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        work[j] += alloc_[i][j];</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    finish[i] = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                    safe_sequence.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(i);</span><br><span class="line">                    found = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (!found) <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 输出安全序列（调试用）</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (safe_sequence.<span class="built_in">size</span>() == <span class="built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;<span class="type">size_t</span>&gt;(num_processes_)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;安全序列: &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> pid : safe_sequence) std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;P&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; pid &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>安全性检查函数</code>实现了判断程序实施某种分配的调度策略是不是安全的。我们用一个<code>bool</code>类型的<code>finish[]</code>数组来存储每一个程序当前的状态，表示模拟序列中有没有运行结束，并把数组初始化为<code>false</code>，代表程序还没有释放资源，正在运行。我们的目标是让<code>finish[]</code>数组的所有元素的结果是1，说明程序已经安全释放，那就说明这个序列是安全的，可以输出。我们再创造一个数组<code>safe_sequence[]</code>来储存每个安全序列的进程的<code>PID</code>，这样既有利于我们最后输出安全序列的顺序，也可以判断整个序列是否是安全的，如果最后<code>safe_sequence[]</code>数组的长度和<code>num_processes_</code>的大小不相等，说明不安全。（<em>注意！<code>num_processes_</code>此处需要强转数据类型。</em>）</p><p>好的，再让我们来分析一下三层循环的结构。我们需要找到安全的序列，那么不能排除“银行”的钱不够（资源不够分配），需要先等“客户”把钱还回来（资源释放），再把“钱借给别的客户”（分配资源）的情况。我们先用一层循环遍历所有的进程，然后在内层循环中遍历所有资源的种类。如果程序的<code>finish</code>态是<code>false</code>，就可以进入内部循环判断是否可以释放，此时创建<code>can_allocate</code>变量，先默认可以释放，如果发现有程序的<code>need_[][]</code>大于<code>work[]</code>即<code>available_[]</code>说明程序不能安全运行结束并释放，需求资源量大于剩余资源量。把<code>can_allocate</code>改成<code>false</code>并直接退出循环，判断<code>can_allocate</code>变量是否为<code>true</code>如果为真，说明变量可以进入序列，把所有资源释放到<code>work[]</code>中，将<code>finish[]</code>状态更新为<code>true</code>，并把进程<code>PID</code>更新到<code>safe_sequence</code>数组中。<br> 经过这种操作我们可以得到一个序列中的元素。此时不难发现，如果只有两层循环我们并不能得到整个有序队列，因为前面释放的资源可以给后面的进程使用，所以最外层需要再加一层循环来找到整个安全队列。我们添加<code>found</code>元素并赋值为<code>false</code>，最外层循环的结尾判断这个<code>found</code>是不是<code>false</code>，如果<code>false</code>说明内层循环并没有找到安全的程序，就可以退出循环了。</p> <figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">BankerAlgorithm::print_state</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="type">const</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;可用资源: &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> res : available_) std::cout &lt;&lt; res &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;\n分配矩阵:\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; row : alloc_) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> val : row) std::cout &lt;&lt; val &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;需求矩阵:\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; row : need_) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> val : row) std::cout &lt;&lt; val &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>状态输出函数</code>代码实现。</p></li><li><p><strong>主函数以及运行结果</strong></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">// 初始化测试数据（题目中的示例）</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> n = <span class="number">5</span>, m = <span class="number">3</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; available = &#123;<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"> std::vector&lt;std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt; alloc = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>&#125;,  <span class="comment">// P1</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">2</span>&#125;,  <span class="comment">// P2</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">5</span>&#125;,  <span class="comment">// P3</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">4</span>&#125;,  <span class="comment">// P4</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">4</span>&#125;   <span class="comment">// P5</span></span><br><span class="line"> &#125;;</span><br><span class="line"> std::vector&lt;std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt; need = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">7</span>&#125;,  <span class="comment">// P1</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>&#125;,  <span class="comment">// P2</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">3</span>&#125;,  <span class="comment">// P3</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>&#125;,  <span class="comment">// P4</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>&#125;   <span class="comment">// P5</span></span><br><span class="line"> &#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="function">BankerAlgorithm <span class="title">banker</span><span class="params">(n, m, available, alloc, need)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"> banker.<span class="built_in">print_state</span>();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">// 测试请求序列</span></span><br><span class="line"> std::vector&lt;std::pair&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt;&gt; requests = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">1</span>, &#123;<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>&#125;&#125;,   <span class="comment">// 请求 a: P2 (注意索引从0开始)</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">3</span>, &#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>&#125;&#125;,   <span class="comment">// 请求 b: P4</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">0</span>, &#123;<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>&#125;&#125;,   <span class="comment">// 请求 c: P1</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;<span class="number">2</span>, &#123;<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">2</span>&#125;&#125;    <span class="comment">// 请求 d: P3</span></span><br><span class="line"> &#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; req : requests) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">int</span> pid = req.first;</span><br><span class="line">     std::vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; request = req.second;</span><br><span class="line">     std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;\n处理请求: P&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; pid &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; 请求资源 (&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> val : request) std::cout &lt;&lt; val &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;)\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">bool</span> success = banker.<span class="built_in">request_resources</span>(pid, request);</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">if</span> (success) banker.<span class="built_in">print_state</span>();</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>以下是运行结果：</p></blockquote><p><img src="/image/Banker.png" alt="Ubuntu上运行结果"></p><p>总结一下，银行家算法通过预判资源分配后的系统状态，确保资源分配的 ‌<strong>安全性‌</strong> 和 <strong>‌高效性‌</strong>，是操作系统课程中经典的死锁避免算法，但是缺点是需要准确了解每个进程的<strong>最大资源需求</strong>，但是现实中进程的请求往往是模糊的，频繁的检查也会导致性能开销。</p></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
